Elsa has a dream of becoming a popular fashion blogger. Today she has got an opportunity to post some latest wedding trends and prove the world that she is blessed with the amazing fashion abilities. The princess needs your support to design a perfect wedding dress and then dress her up with that outfit. Would you guide her to select some fashionable wedding outfits? Join Wedding Facebook Blog game and be prepared to dress her up and take some photos for the blog post!
Remember it is a matter of proving her best, so putting your best fashion sense will only be required to get her noticed online in this brand new dressing game. Check out the latest wedding trends before starting this fun! Give her a white color gown or a blue color dress with some flowers from top to bottom or a red color gown with some flair below thigh in this html5 princess dress up game! Choose a pair of matching blue color, golden color or silver color sandals!
Complete the look of a wedding girl with sparkling golden or silver color jewelry! A bouquet with orange color or red, pink and yellow color or light and dark blue color flowers will give her an awesome bridal look. Select a lovely golden or silver color handbag and give it to the princess when she prepares to get a bridal appearance! Click the last option to change the background of this cool girls game! Take a picture of that look and get ready to dress your girl! Do not forget to take the picture of the final look of your girl. Good luck to have fun in our best girls games!
